    MODULE=lunar-tools
   VERSION=2026.7
    SOURCE=$MODULE-$VERSION-i686.tar.xz
SOURCE_URL=https://github.com/lunar-linux/lunar-tools/releases/download/$VERSION
SOURCE_VFY=sha256:100fd6030dab2a3dcd45fc741ddf7304bfc2621d85c5c0693dc53af38dff3b41
  WEB_SITE=http://lunar-linux.org/
   ENTERED=20041029
   UPDATED=20260319
     SHORT="A collection of lunar tools"

cat << EOF
Lunar-tools is a package with non-vital tools that help you perform
certain system tasks. Currently it lists the following tools:

lnet           network administration tool
lservices      start/stop and add/remove startup services
luser          user and group administration tool
lids           file integrity and permission monitoring tool
lmodules       handle your kernel modules
clad           cluster administration tool
ltime          set your timezone
installkernel  installs kernels using the kernel 'make install'
llint          module linting tool
EOF
